{"tema":12,"idioma":"en","titulo":"Presente continuo y have got","regla":"El presente continuo (algo que pasa ahora): am/is/are + verbo-ing: 'I'm wearing jeans', 'She is reading'. 'Have got' expresa posesión: 'I've got a jacket' = 'I have a jacket'.","pronunciacion":"La terminación -ing siempre suena 'ing', nunca 'in': wearing, no 'wearin'.","trampa":"El continuo necesita el verbo 'to be' + -ing: 'she is wearing', no 'she wearing'.","ejemplos":[{"frase":"I'm wearing a jacket.","traduccion":"Llevo puesta una chaqueta.","comoSeLee":"aim uéring e yáket"},{"frase":"She is reading.","traduccion":"Ella está leyendo.","comoSeLee":"shi is ríding"},{"frase":"I've got a new phone.","traduccion":"Tengo un teléfono nuevo.","comoSeLee":"aiv gat e niú fon"}],"ejercicios":[{"tipo":"hueco","enunciado":"I ___ wearing jeans. (to be)","respuesta":"am","aceptadas":["'m"]},{"tipo":"hueco","enunciado":"She is ___ a book. (read)","respuesta":"reading"},{"tipo":"hueco","enunciado":"I've ___ a jacket. (posesión)","respuesta":"got"},{"tipo":"hueco","enunciado":"They ___ playing football. (to be)","respuesta":"are","aceptadas":["'re"]},{"tipo":"opcion_multiple","enunciado":"Gerundio de 'wear':","opciones":["wearing","weared","wears"],"respuesta":"wearing"},{"tipo":"opcion_multiple","enunciado":"She ___ a dress.","opciones":["is wearing","wearing","wears wearing"],"respuesta":"is wearing"},{"tipo":"opcion_multiple","enunciado":"'Tengo una mochila' =","opciones":["I've got a bag","I got a bag","I has got a bag"],"respuesta":"I've got a bag"},{"tipo":"ordenar","enunciado":"Ordena: llevo puesta una chaqueta.","opciones":["I","am","wearing","a","jacket"],"respuesta":"I am wearing a jacket"},{"tipo":"ordenar","enunciado":"Ordena: ella está leyendo un libro.","opciones":["she","is","reading","a","book"],"respuesta":"she is reading a book"},{"tipo":"ordenar","enunciado":"Ordena: tengo un teléfono nuevo.","opciones":["I","have","got","a","new","phone"],"respuesta":"I have got a new phone"},{"tipo":"corregir_error","enunciado":"She wearing a dress.","respuesta":"She is wearing a dress."},{"tipo":"corregir_error","enunciado":"I am wear a hat.","respuesta":"I am wearing a hat."},{"tipo":"corregir_error","enunciado":"They is playing.","respuesta":"They are playing."},{"tipo":"traducir","enunciado":"Ella está leyendo.","respuesta":"She is reading.","aceptadas":["she is reading"]},{"tipo":"traducir","enunciado":"Tengo un teléfono nuevo.","respuesta":"I've got a new phone.","aceptadas":["i have got a new phone","i have a new phone"]}]}
